    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a willing creature, granting it an elemental charge. Choose acid, cold, fire, lightning, poison or sonic. For the duration, a creature can use an action to expel energy of the chosen type in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking [[/r 3d6]] damage of the chosen type on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Overcharge Tech.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a tech slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p>",
